{"ts":"2026-05-16T22:07:27.879Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-tzwy"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Drastically improve GitHub runner time and resource usage (free-tier only)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Current CI per-commit cost: 5 matrix jobs running ~11-12min each (~700s wall). Goal: cut total runner minutes 40-60% without losing test coverage, platform matrix, or quality gates. Constraint: free-tier GitHub features only - no paid runners, no GitHub Hosted Larger Runners. Approach: skip-on-doc-only, eliminate duplicate test runs, smaller PR matrix, tsbuildinfo incremental cache, parallelize gates into their own short job, cache vitest/lancedb/sentry caches between runs."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":0},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["ci","cost","free-tier","github-actions","performance","pm-cli"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-16T22:07:27.879Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-16T22:07:27.879Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Average CI duration per push/PR cut by >=40%; total runner minutes per PR cut by >=50% on common docs-only or single-file PRs; full matrix still runs on main push; coverage gate, static quality gate, plugin smoke tests still gating; pnpm audit/security:scan still gating; no paid GitHub features used; CI is green on the change."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-rnpb"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"03a36e0a6195170999207e7557bfa85f42150b4de982f97fe6119b37e9859344","message":""}
